column10: u'Requests that a backup of the specified key be downloaded to the client.  The Key Backup operation exports a key from Azure Key Vault in a protected form. Note that this operation does NOT return key material in a form that can be used outside the Azure Key Vault system
column11: the returned key material is either protected to a Azure Key Vault HSM or to Azure Key Vault itself. The intent of this operation is to allow a client to GENERATE a key in one Azure Key Vault instance
column13: and then RESTORE it into another Azure Key Vault instance. The BACKUP operation may be used to export
column15: any key type from Azure Key Vault. Individual versions of a key cannot be backed up. BACKUP / RESTORE can be performed within geographical boundaries only
column16: meaning that a BACKUP from one geographical area cannot be restored to another geographical area. For example
column17: a backup from the US geographical area cannot be restored in an EU geographical area.']
